{"calories":"720","carbs":68,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eChef Giuseppe wows us with yet another luxurious risotto—this time featuring two forms of both mushrooms and cheese. He infuses warm broth with ground and dried porcini mushrooms, then roasts and sautés creminis for stirring into the finished dish. Nutty aged Gruyère adds richness, along with dollops of chive-laced mascarpone cheese.\u003c/p\u003e","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"4f94dea24a","fat":40,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69139/c62MWiL8RVupn6CJMVRB_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Mascarpone__Gruye_re__and_Chives_006_HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69139/hero_c62MWiL8RVupn6CJMVRB_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Mascarpone__Gruye_re__and_Chives_006_HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69139/menu_small_c62MWiL8RVupn6CJMVRB_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Mascarpone__Gruye_re__and_Chives_006_HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69139/small_square_c62MWiL8RVupn6CJMVRB_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Mascarpone__Gruye_re__and_Chives_006_HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69139/medium_square_c62MWiL8RVupn6CJMVRB_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Mascarpone__Gruye_re__and_Chives_006_HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69139/recipe_profile_page_c62MWiL8RVupn6CJMVRB_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Mascarpone__Gruye_re__and_Chives_006_HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"ma